{
  "texts": [
    "Our work bridges critical gaps by:",
    "• Establishing validity metrics beyond answer correctness, focusing on medical reasoning ability.",
    "We evaluate not just *what* the LLM answers, but *how* it arrives at that answer, analyzing the steps in its reasoning process.",
    "This goes beyond simple accuracy metrics to assess the quality and appropriateness of the reasoning itself.",
    "• Identifying high-risk error patterns requiring mitigation, such as anchoring bias, protocol violations, and misinterpretations of lab values."
  ]
}